Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 想和我们自拍就说\N{\fs38}Yeah, like, if you ever want to take a selfie --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 还是朋友吧\N{\fs38}So, are we cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 谢谢 先生们\N{\fs38}PRESIDENT: Yes. Thank you, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啥来着\N{\fs38}I told you, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊Morty 谈得真不错\N{\fs38}I’m impressed, Morty. That went really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都给我稳住\N{\fs38}Everybody, get ahold of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生 对于Rick和Morty我们有什么新的政策\N{\fs38}Sir, what is our new Rick and Morty policy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的政策是 我们从来不需要他们 以后也不\N{\fs38}Our policy is, we never needed them and never will again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.77,0:05:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 让我们庆祝独立 正式脱离Rick和Morty\N{\fs38}Today, we celebrate our independence from Rick and Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人都出去\N{\fs38}Everyone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*怎么能逃离你的爱*\N{\fs38}How can I move on from your love?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春季新款尽在服饰商场 服装大减价正在进行时\N{\fs38}MAN: All this spring at Clothes Mart, there’s a clothes sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.75,0:05:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到楼下服装区来看看吧\N{\fs38}Come on down to the clothes section.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:23.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不过是试着玩儿的 我知道不能买这件衣服\N{\fs38}I just put it on for fun. I know I can’t buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 别胡说了 你看起来真美 人生哪得长少年\N{\fs38}Oh, come on. You look great! You’re only young once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.26,0:05:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要保证 如果有什么严重的后果\N{\fs38}Just promise, if the results are too strong
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会采取保护措施\N{\fs38}you’ll use protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 谢谢\N{\fs38}Really?! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候变得这么开放了 - 我也不知道\N{\fs38}When did you get rad? -l don’t know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我适应了离婚的事 一切都是全新的了\N{\fs38}Maybe I adjusted to the divorce and everything’s new.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实是 之前有一阵子\N{\fs38}I’ll say. I couldn’t stand you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:40.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能忍受你的时间不超过一小时\N{\fs38}for more than an hour at a time before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意 无意冒犯\N{\fs38}No -- No offense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你这样 太棒了 你就像变了一个人\N{\fs38}I like it. It’s great. You’re like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊\N{\fs38}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变了一个人\N{\fs38}Different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:06:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑 快跑 啊啊啊\N{\fs38}Vamos! Vamos! Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这个怎么样 Morty\N{\fs38}How do you like that, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 就像"我的世界"一样\N{\fs38}Whoa! Just like “Minecraft”!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 一种具有核能力的小型物种\N{\fs38}Ooh, a tiny nuclear-capable species
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚在亚马逊被人发现\N{\fs38}just got discovered in the Amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们先去会会\N{\fs38}Let’s go make first contact
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.94,0:06:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以免其他人捷足先登\N{\fs38}before someone else gets all their shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个怎么办\N{\fs38}What about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,南方公园4年前就玩过了 Morty\N{\fs38}South Park did it four years ago, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们好快啊\N{\fs38}They’re fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者说是我们慢了\N{\fs38}Or we’re slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:19.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 各位\N{\fs38}Don’t do it, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然搞不好会有"巴十西万"人的伤亡\N{\fs38}The casualties would be in the “Brazilians”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们是巴西人\N{\fs38}because you’re Brazilian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.27,0:06:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这既是威胁 又一语双关\N{\fs38}It's a threat and a pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:26.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么没人懂我的意思\N{\fs38}Nobody gets me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国人来了 快跑\N{\fs38}Americanos! Pressa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 你好啊 Rick 你也在这儿\N{\fs38}Oh. Hello, Rick. You’re here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.46,0:06:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那看来这的确是一场全球性危机\N{\fs38}I guess this is a global crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 天哪\N{\fs38}Oh, God. Uh, Mr. President
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统先生 我和Morty已经把场面控制住了\N{\fs38}Morty and I have the situation covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.55,0:06:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确信你们做到了\N{\fs38}I’m sure you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走人吧 - 走人\N{\fs38}Dismissed. -Dismissed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 走人吧\N{\fs38}Yeah, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.06,0:07:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不需要你们 你们走吧 没人会在意的\N{\fs38}Not needed here. You can leave and nobody will care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.43,0:07:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前从来没听过这句话吗\N{\fs38}Have you never heard that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.44,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道怎么消除这种威胁吗\N{\fs38}Do you even know how to take out this kind of threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不打算消除威胁\N{\fs38}We’re not taking it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要缩小自己 通过外交途径接触它们\N{\fs38}We’re going to shrink down and approach them diplomatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就靠吃药丸缩身 - 你俩怎么还在\N{\fs38}RICK: You shrink with pills? -Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你难道不应该去另一个版本的地球\N{\fs38}Shouldn’t you be going down to your next version of Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带着你这个自拍狂魔加追星狂人小跟班\N{\fs38}with your selfie-craving star-fucker sidekick?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.08,0:07:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 我们有权利在这儿\N{\fs38}Whoa! -We’re allowed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.74,0:07:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又不是亚马逊总统\N{\fs38}You aren’t president of the Amazon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 我在学校学过你的职责\N{\fs38}Yeah, I learned about your job in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是人民公仆\N{\fs38}You’re a civil servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照理说我们是你老板\N{\fs38}We’re technically your boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.75,0:07:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 得了吧 Morty\N{\fs38}Oh, please, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你上的税和你的屌毛一样少得可怜\N{\fs38}You pay as many taxes as you have pubes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 我有屌毛 阴屁司令\N{\fs38}Oh, I got pubes, Commander-in-Queef.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.30,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想数一数吗 - 阴屁司令\N{\fs38}Y-You want to count them? -Commander-in-Queef.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 快上\N{\fs38}That’s it! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.80,0:07:37.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认出这种稀有元素桑切斯金属了吗\N{\fs38}Recognize the rare element Sanchez-eum?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们对Rick级别的突发事件已经做了一段时间的准备\N{\fs38}We’ve been preparing for a Ricklevel eventuality for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说是你一直在命令别人做准备\N{\fs38}You mean you’ve been ordering other people to prepare for it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本人在和平峰会干坐着呢吧\N{\fs38}while you sat on your ass at peace summits.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:45.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和平峰会意义重大\N{\fs38}Peace summits are important!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.78,0:07:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 是啊 成果喜人呢\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah! They work great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.79,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都快被和平淹没了\N{\fs38}We’re really drowning in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这弱逼 - 你才弱逼\N{\fs38}You suck! -You suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法特遣队 准备开始缩小\N{\fs38}Task Force Alpha, prepare to shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法特遣队有没有医保啊\N{\fs38}Is there a Task Force Alpha health plan, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那些药丸是根据亚原子压缩原理制成的\N{\fs38}Because if those pills are based on subatomic compression
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你直接从蘑菇云中间走过去\N{\fs38}you could get a more curable cancer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.66,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得的癌症都要比吃这个好治一点儿\N{\fs38}just walking through the mushroom clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去你妈的 我来吃\N{\fs38}God damn it! I’ll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.66,0:08:05.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿尔法特遣队被解散了\N{\fs38}Whoa. -Task Force Alpha is disbanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩不再是美国人了\N{\fs38}And you two aren’t American anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有权这样做 你们被流放了\N{\fs38}I can say that. You’re expatriated!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们再踏入祖国的国土\N{\fs38}If you step foot on homeland soil again
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就当成侵略来处理\N{\fs38}Ill treat it as an invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按说这个过程会很痛苦吗\N{\fs38}Is this supposed to be painful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旁边看的人很痛苦\N{\fs38}Painful to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.01,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么垃圾缩小技术\N{\fs38}Oh, such lame shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的衣服还是原来的大小\N{\fs38}Oh, his clothes stay the same size?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.01,0:08:22.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,70年代缩小术 一人份\N{\fs38}70s shrinking, party of one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我渐渐变小的屁股去吧\N{\fs38}Eat my shrinking ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他走了 好吧 Morty 我们离开这儿吧\N{\fs38}There he goes. All right. Let’s get out of here, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么\N{\fs38}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桑切斯金属是我瞎编的 傻逼们\N{\fs38}I made Sanchez-eum up, dumbasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别在维基百科上读到什么都信啊\N{\fs38}Don’t believe everything you read on Wikipedia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.24,0:08:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戒卫解除\N{\fs38}Stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.17,0:08:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不怕海盗\N{\fs38}He’s not afraid of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.07,0:08:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑Morty 怕海盗是真的\N{\fs38}Oh! Run, Morty! That part was true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 我现在没空讲话 - 你什么时候可以咯\N{\fs38}I-I can’t talk now, sweetie. -Oh, when can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.11,0:09:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有道理 什么事儿\N{\fs38}Good point. What’s up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得不久之前你说过吗 如果我想的话\N{\fs38}Remember a little while ago when you said that, if I wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.72,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以 离开地球在无尽的宇宙中漫游啥的\N{\fs38}I could, like, leave Earth and wander the infinite cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来寻找真正的自我而且永远没人会发现我已经离开了\N{\fs38}to figure out who I am and that nobody would ever know I’d left
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你可以用一个克隆人来代替我\N{\fs38}because you could replace me with a clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是那个克隆人吗\N{\fs38}Mm-hmm. -Am I the clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 什么 - 我是克隆人吗\N{\fs38}Sorry. What? -Am I the clone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.19,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的我是不是选择了离开 而我自认为我选择了留下\N{\fs38}Did the real me choose to leave, and I only think I chose to stay
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为我必须这样想\N{\fs38}because that’s what I need to think
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我就是那个替代的克隆Beth\N{\fs38}because I’m the replacement Beth?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 - 好吧\N{\fs38}No. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 还有一件事 如果我是克隆人的话 你会告诉我吗\N{\fs38}Wait. And one more thing.If I were a clone, would you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth当 当聪明人变得幸福的时候\N{\fs38}Beth, you know, when -- when smart people get happy
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们就认不清自己了\N{\fs38}they sTop recognizing themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而你非常聪明 因为你是我的女儿\N{\fs38}And you are very smart because you’re very much my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 你是对的 我很抱歉\N{\fs38}Oh, God. You’re right. I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 爸爸\N{\fs38}Thank you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧 - 是的\N{\fs38}All good? - TotaIly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.23,0:09:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事了\N{\fs38}I’m fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.63,0:09:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认一下\N{\fs38}And just to be sure,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.18,0:09:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是在假装相信你是真Beth吧\N{\fs38}you’re not pretending to be convinced you’re real
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.76,0:09:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你其实认为自己是个克隆人\N{\fs38}because you’re actually convinced you’re a clone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后你现在害怕自己认识到自己是克隆人\N{\fs38}and you’re now terrified that becoming self-aware
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,代表我必须除掉你\N{\fs38}would mean I’d have to terminate you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 - 好吧 很高兴我能帮上忙\N{\fs38}No. -RICK: Okay. Glad I could help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.31,0:09:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿见\N{\fs38}See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.74,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该往哪儿开\N{\fs38}Where do I go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么 什么什么 这是什么意思\N{\fs38}What does th-- What -- What -- What -- What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:10.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这毫无意义\N{\fs38}This means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往前开然后停车\N{\fs38}Pull forward and park.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你倒是说啊 妈的\N{\fs38}Then say that, God damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起\N{\fs38}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天过得不顺\N{\fs38}Bad day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是超级巨人族的总统\N{\fs38}I am Presidentress of the Mega Gargantuans.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在发现自己很小之前取了这个名字\N{\fs38}We named ourselves before learning we were small.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总统女士 我是美国总统\N{\fs38}Madam Presidentress, I’m President of America
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.89,0:10:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,基本等于全球总统\N{\fs38}which is basically the world
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你别说是我说的\N{\fs38}but you didn’t hear that from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我前来 - 我知道你是谁\N{\fs38}I’ve come to -- -I know who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经同意休战了\N{\fs38}We’ve already agreed to a ceasefire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与你的大使Rick和Morty谈过了\N{\fs38}with your ambassadors, Rick and Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick和Morty来过了吗 - 他们当然来过了\N{\fs38}Rick and Morty were here? -Of course they were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.73,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可以瞬间变小 还能瞬移\N{\fs38}They can shrink instantly and teleport.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.61,0:10:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们让我给你这个\N{\fs38}They told me to give you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说随着你的癌症药丸药效消失\N{\fs38}They said it will stretch as your cancer pill wears off
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身体尴尬地以老电影里的速度变大时 衣服会撑大\N{\fs38}and your body awkwardly enlarges at the rate of a ‘50s movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有裤子吗\N{\fs38}Are there pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.95,0:10:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说你会只想要一件衣服的\N{\fs38}They said you’d prefer just a shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.08,0:10:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是因为你有乱晃鸡巴的需求\N{\fs38}Apparently, you have a need to swing your dick around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick和Morty逃走了\N{\fs38}Rick and Morty escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.04,0:10:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废话 带我去五角大楼\N{\fs38}No shit. Take me to the Pentagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要和Rick和Morty开战\N{\fs38}We’re at war with Rick and Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你想顺道去下白宫吗\N{\fs38}You’ll want to make a sTop at the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在五角大楼有裤子 Rhonda 合同里写着呢\N{\fs38}I have pants at the Pentagon, Rhonda. It’s in my contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说你需要召开新闻发布会\N{\fs38}I mean you need to call a press conference.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.47,0:11:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以色列和巴勒斯坦宣布永久停火\N{\fs38}Israel and Palestine have announced a permanent ceasefire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 - 他们签署了一个叫作\N{\fs38}What? -They signed something called
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"挺明白的事儿想想就知道"协议\N{\fs38}“The Pretty Obvious If You Think About It” accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是一名匿名的美国外交官\N{\fs38}Apparently, an anonymous American diplomat
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带他们去了一个"星战"主题酒吧\N{\fs38}took them to a “Star Wars” cantina,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:19.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们用激光水烟抽了能增强认知视野的外星费洛蒙\N{\fs38}where they smoked perspective-enhancing alien pheromones through a laser hookah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是认为这是普京干的\N{\fs38}I still say it has to be Putin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Rick和Morty干的 你傻驴啊\N{\fs38}It was Rick and Morty, you fucking dunce!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.15,0:11:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过功劳都是你领了 先生\N{\fs38}But you’re getting the credit, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的民众支持率刚刚达到了100%\N{\fs38}Your approval rating just hit 100%.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick和Morty为什么要这么做\N{\fs38}Why would Rick and Morty want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他们是混球\N{\fs38}Because they’re assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.35,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢大家的称赞 但我们今天的成就归功于整个团队\N{\fs38}I’m flattered, but it takes a whole team to achieve what we did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况呢 - 他们没有回家 先生\N{\fs38}Well? - They haven’t been back home, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在监视每个他们可能出现的地点\N{\fs38}We’ve got every possible location under surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.80,0:11:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的 他们就在这儿\N{\fs38}God damn it! They’re right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在这里 妈的 - 红色警报 需要支援\N{\fs38}They’re here, God damn it! -Code Red! We need backup!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家放松\N{\fs38}Everybody relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在你不能炸掉或监控的唯一房间等你而已\N{\fs38}Just waiting for you in the only room you can’t blow up or spy on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会为你改变时间线\N{\fs38}So, we’re not changing timelines for you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在你得到你想要的了\N{\fs38}but now you have everything you want
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以无视我们的存在\N{\fs38}so you can forget we exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也能无视你的存在\N{\fs38}and we’ll return the favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能写条短信说吗\N{\fs38}You couldn’t say that in a text?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 因为我们不会再见面了 我的\N{\fs38}Well, since we won’t be seeing each other again, my --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.54,0:12:00.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伙计们 我们懂 是红色警报 够了\N{\fs38}Guys, we get it. It’s a Code Red. Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我孙子为你的事跑前跑后\N{\fs38}My grandson has worked hard for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他有权和你合影自拍一张\N{\fs38}and I feel like he’s earned a selfie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.30,0:12:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 现在我无所谓拍不拍的\N{\fs38}Honestly, I could take it or leave it at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要拍\N{\fs38}You’re taking it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.18,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你这是什么大学兄弟会显摆地位的招啊\N{\fs38}No. What kind of fratty-ass status move is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.18,0:12:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出我的办公室\N{\fs38}Get out of my office!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我靠 你真那么固执吗\N{\fs38}SeriousIy? You’re that stubborn?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才固执 我是在保护我的国家\N{\fs38}He’s the stubborn one. I’m protecting my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免受自拍的侵犯吗\N{\fs38}Uh, from selfies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.02,0:12:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免于屈从敌对力量\N{\fs38}From subordination to hostile powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.63,0:12:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那中国知道你这强硬的态度吗\N{\fs38}Uh, does China know about that deal-breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中国不会跑来骑在白宫头上拉屎撒尿\N{\fs38}China doesn’t piss on the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哦 他们为什么会 那很费钱吧\N{\fs38}Well, why would they? I’m sure it was expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.98,0:12:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚 - 没自拍就不走\N{\fs38}Get out. -Not without a selfie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮捕 - 小伙 你有权不服从他的命令\N{\fs38}Arrest them. - Son, you have a right to refuse his order
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证只要摸我一下 你就会死\N{\fs38}and I guarantee you’re going to die if you touch me
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.45,0:12:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么来生 一切直接陷入黑暗\N{\fs38}and there’s no afterlife. Everything just goes black.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么做\N{\fs38}Don’t do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.65,0:12:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 Rick - 好吧\N{\fs38}Whoa, Rick! -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事\N{\fs38}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.70,0:12:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死亡 - 哪种\N{\fs38}Death. -What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.57,0:12:34.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即刻 - 可是都没声音啊\N{\fs38}Instant. -There was no sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就死了 - 嗯 很可怕\N{\fs38}He just died. -Yeah, terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.67,0:12:38.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这看着是很可怕\N{\fs38}It’s a terrifying thing to watch happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫威慑\N{\fs38}It’s called a deterrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.38,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能只把他打晕吗\N{\fs38}You couldn’t just knock him out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.88,0:12:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打晕怎么能算威慑呢\N{\fs38}How is knocking out a deterrent?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:43.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都想被打晕\N{\fs38}Everyone wants to be knocked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.96,0:12:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人想死\N{\fs38}Nobody wants to be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在美国总统办公室里杀了人\N{\fs38}You committed murder in the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.80,0:12:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你不能离开 - 没事\N{\fs38}Now you can’t leave. -That’s fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了要一起自拍再走\N{\fs38}I said I’m not leaving without a selfie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我不需要跟总统一起自拍\N{\fs38}Uh, I don’t need a selfie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:51.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会跟你自拍的\N{\fs38}And I’m saying you aren’t getting one
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.01,0:12:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也走不了了\N{\fs38}and you aren’t leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们达成一致了 - 是的 不\N{\fs38}So we agree? -Yes. No. We disagree
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.56,0:12:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们意见不统一 因为你想要拿到合照然后离开\N{\fs38}because you think you’re getting a selfie and leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.52,0:12:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会拿到合照吗\N{\fs38}Am I getting a selfie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:12:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不 - 那我绝不走\N{\fs38}Never. -Then I’m never leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 - 看吧\N{\fs38}Exactly. -See?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人能开枪杀了他吗\N{\fs38}Does anyone have a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.93,0:13:03.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有 有九个人可以 我能给你们展示一下\N{\fs38}Yes, nine people. I can show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不建议\N{\fs38}But I wouldn’t recommend --
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪\N{\fs38}Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.49,0:13:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天 你们太蠢了\N{\fs38}God, you are dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带总统离开这里\N{\fs38}Get the President out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是馊主意 - 等等 为什么\N{\fs38}Bad idea. -Wait. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.45,0:13:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这里没有他们不能杀的人\N{\fs38}Because if there isn’t someone in here that they’re not supposed to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.04,0:13:15.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会在试图杀我的过程中把这地方都砸了\N{\fs38}they’re going to wreck the place trying to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:17.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你活着 无论你在哪儿\N{\fs38}As long as you live, no matter where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你不是在跟他的合照里面\N{\fs38}if it isn’t in a selfie with him
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会在这儿\N{\fs38}I’ll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.54,0:13:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天 他又不是神\N{\fs38}Jesus! He’s not a fucking god!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.80,0:13:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道我是什么\N{\fs38}You don’t know what I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你更不知道我能做什么\N{\fs38}And you don’t know what I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天 冷 冷静点 Rick\N{\fs38}Geez, it’s -- it’s cool, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这儿的神秘博士\N{\fs38}I’m Doctor Who in this motherfucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以是个克隆 我可以是个全息影像\N{\fs38}I could be a clone. I could be a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.01,0:13:31.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都可以是克隆\N{\fs38}We could be clones controlled by robots
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被正在操你妈的真正的Rick和Morty\N{\fs38}controlled with special headsets
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用头戴的特别设备操控的\N{\fs38}that the real Rick and Morty are wearing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人所操控的克隆\N{\fs38}while they’re fucking your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你\N{\fs38}I’m going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就来奥利街312号\N{\fs38}Then come to 312 Olive Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我妈现在的地址吗\N{\fs38}Is that her address?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道 因为你是个坏儿子\N{\fs38}You don’t know because you’re a bad son!
