Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是在毁掉一个真正的家\N{\fs38}But you’re killing a real family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.94,0:19:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 你能不能不要这样做 离开就好\N{\fs38}And instead of doing that, will you just go away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有无限的时间线吗\N{\fs38}Aren’t there, like, infinite timelines?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.11,0:19:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能去到一个我不知道我是克隆体的世界\N{\fs38}Can’t you just move to one where I don’t know I’m a clone
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个完全一致的另一个版本的\N{\fs38}and where a different but identical version
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真正的反社会的疯女儿\N{\fs38}of your authentic sociopathic crazy bitch
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让你继续为之骄傲\N{\fs38}of a daughter can keep making you proud
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.53,0:19:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她愿意漂泊天际\N{\fs38}by being somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Beth 你个疯子 你就是我女儿\N{\fs38}Beth, you crazy bitch. You’re my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我带枪来是要杀Jerry\N{\fs38}I brought this here to kill Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老天爷 - 我的天\N{\fs38}Oh, my God! -Jesus Christ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.25,0:19:39.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 你赢了 Jerry 你赢了\N{\fs38}Yeah. Yeah, yeah. You win, Jerry. You win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多的才智也不能阻止你的那些愚蠢庸碌和空虚\N{\fs38}No amount of genius can sTop your dumb mediocre vacuous roots
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把根扎进你周围所有的人和事\N{\fs38}from digging into everything and everyone around you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抽干他们所有躲掉你的能力\N{\fs38}and draining them of any ability to fend you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要在过去让你说出这些可不容易\N{\fs38}Well, it couldn’t have been easy for you to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激\N{\fs38}I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 我的传送枪呢\N{\fs38}Morty, where’s my portal gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.03,0:19:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开这儿吧\N{\fs38}Let’s get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要待在这儿 Rick\N{\fs38}I’m staying here, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.94,0:19:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是 啊\N{\fs38}Are you -- Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:57.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人明白\N{\fs38}Nobody gets it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.98,0:19:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切你认为重要的事情都不重要\N{\fs38}Nothing you think matters matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这没什么特殊的\N{\fs38}This isn’t special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些发生了无数次\N{\fs38}This -- This is happening infinite times
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在无数个现实当中\N{\fs38}across infinite realities.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.45,0:20:05.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括这个吗\N{\fs38}Including this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.95,0:20:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs38}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.45,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说我主观上觉得你这招不好笑\N{\fs38}Which is not to say that, subjectively, it wasn’t funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.45,0:20:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要留在这儿吗\N{\fs38}Are you going to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有无数条时间线 Morty\N{\fs38}There’s infinite timelines, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.08,0:20:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为什么还要待在这里 我在这儿把白宫闹了个底朝天\N{\fs38}Why would I stay in the one where I trashed the White House
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了美国公敌\N{\fs38}became an enemy of America
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还成了我的呆子家庭里地位最底下的人\N{\fs38}and the lowest-status character in my idiot family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了那个屁可以吗\N{\fs38}Because of the fart?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.67,0:20:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那儿还有点碎砖块\N{\fs38}There’s still some rubble over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为你从没弄明白\N{\fs38}I don’t think you’ve ever understood
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,内务部长到底是干什么的\N{\fs38}what “Secretary of the Interior” means!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.22,0:20:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 总统先生 我是Rick Sanchez\N{\fs38}Hi, Mr. President. I’m Rick Sanchez
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.27,0:20:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不是这次捣乱的那个\N{\fs38}but not the one that did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们Rick游历于无穷宇宙中 而且会和彼此交换位置\N{\fs38}We Ricks travel the infinite and switch places with each other
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像寄居蟹 我觉得\N{\fs38}like hermit crabs, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是飞钓Rick\N{\fs38}I’m Fly Fishing Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.90,0:20:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您可以把我\N{\fs38}You can distinguish me from the Rick
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和那个跟您打了一架的Rick区分开来\N{\fs38}that you had a falling-out with
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通过我对飞钓的热爱和我戴的帽子\N{\fs38}by my fly-fishing enthusiasm and accompanying hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望我能出一份力\N{\fs38}I hope I can be of service
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果 呃 你发现这颗星球处于危险中的话\N{\fs38}if, uh, you ever find the planet to be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.70,0:20:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交个朋友\N{\fs38}Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:53.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来不错\N{\fs38}Sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们 晚餐来了\N{\fs38}Kids, dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:20:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我点了熊猫中餐外卖\N{\fs38}I got Panda Express!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.50,0:20:57.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你买了香甜鸡吗\N{\fs38}Did you get sugar chicken?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们差不多只有这个吧\N{\fs38}That’s kind of the only thing they have.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱熊猫中餐外卖 多谢老妈\N{\fs38}I love Panda E! Thanks, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.21,0:21:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望待会儿能尝尝你的香甜鸡\N{\fs38}I’m hoping to get a piece of your sugar chicken later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌\N{\fs38}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你的脑残帽子 傻逼\N{\fs38}Here’s your stupid hat, dipshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.63,0:21:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸 你不能再那样和Jerry说话了\N{\fs38}Dad, you can’t talk to Jerry that way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在是个真正的家庭了\N{\fs38}We’re a real family now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.68,0:21:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从很多意义上来讲 事情会变得和第一季一样\N{\fs38}In many ways, things will be like Season 1
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是更精简流畅\N{\fs38}but more streamlined.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在Jerry和我是幸福的已婚父母\N{\fs38}Now Jerry and I are happily married parents
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有我因为对你离开的恐惧而激发的想法\N{\fs38}and the idea that I was motivated
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都烟消云散了\N{\fs38}by a fear of you leaving can be eschewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烟消云散 你从来没用过这个词\N{\fs38}Eschewed? You’ve never used that word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能你真是个克隆人\N{\fs38}Maybe you are a clone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.61,0:21:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick又不会告诉我们\N{\fs38}It’s not like Rick would tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.44,0:22:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢咦 真是精彩的一季\N{\fs38}Ooh-wee! What a season!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思我再没出场 但是我结婚了\N{\fs38}Sorry I never showed up, but I got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了小孩儿\N{\fs38}I had a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回到了学校 拿到了我的高中同等学学学历\N{\fs38}I went back to school and got my G-E-E-E-D.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在等待的时候做了什么呢\N{\fs38}What did you do while you were waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你不只是到处乱搞 浪费生命\N{\fs38}Hopefully you didn’t just fuck around and waste your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢咦\N{\fs38}Ooh-wee!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.83,0:22:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第四季见 大概要很长的时间\N{\fs38}See you for Season 4 in, like, a really long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.55,0:22:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能会长出圣诞老人那样的大白胡子\N{\fs38}I might even have a big white Santa Claus beard
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.76,0:22:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 还有 还有一\N{\fs38}and -- and -- and a --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:34.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有一群孙子\N{\fs38}and a couple of grandkids
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之类之类的\N{\fs38}and all that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.10,0:22:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道什么时间能见 先再见吧\N{\fs38}See you -- See you then!
